// I was thinking we could use a number pad to prompt grid placement because the number pad is a 3x3 grid
// (ex. Numpad 7 is upper left cone node, Numpad 2 is bottom middle hybrid node, Numpad 5 is middle cube node)

// Top cone nodes are at 3' 10", Middle cone nodes are at 2' 10"

