  // No: Do not execute code
  // Yes: Numpad key pressed?
    // No:
      // Wait for input
    // Numpad 1, Numpad 4, or Numpad 7:
      // Disable movement control
      // Robot moves to the left so that the arm is oriented to place on the left
      // Numpad 1, 4, or 7 pressed?
        // Numpad 1: Arm moves to place on bottom level, release grip, maneuver arm back
        // Numpad 4: Arm moves to place on middle level, release grip, maneuver arm back
        // Numpad 7: Arm moves to place on top level, release grip, maneuver arm back
    // Numpad 3, Numpad 6, or Numpad 9:
      // Robot moves to the right so that the arm is oriented to place on the right
      // Disable movement control
      // Numpad 3, 6, or 9 pressed?
        // Numpad 3: Arm moves to place on bottom level, release grip, maneuver arm back
        // Numpad 6: Arm moves to place on middle level, release grip, maneuver arm back
        // Numpad 9: Arm moves to place on top level, release grip, maneuver arm back
    // Numpad 2, Numpad 5, or Numpad 8?
      // Disable movement control
      // Numpad 2, 5, or 8 pressed?
        // Numpad 2: Execute cube placement for bottom level
